Select Accept to consent or Reject to decline non-essential cookies for this use. You can update your choices at any time in your settings.

Receiving the top innovation award after 21 years in the industry is an incredible honor. My journey has been shaped by experience, creativity, good intention, consistency and a touch of good luck. Grateful to Infineon, supervisors, mentors and colleagues. Join us for what lies ahead in Infineon driving decarbonization and digitalization!
